^ Trina Solar takes top spot amongst PV module suppliers, last access 30 April 2015
^ http://washpost.bloomberg.com/Story?docId=1376-O8R8ER6K50Y601-184KBO46SV3927Q402P85OE5G9#
^ Trina Solar 2013 Sustainable Development Report, last access 29 April 2015
^ Trina Solar WEEE Directive compliance, last access 29 April 2015
^ Solar Scorecard 2012, last access 29 April 2015
^ Solar Scorecard 2013, last access 29 April 2015
^ Solar Scorecard 2014, last access 29 April 2015
^ Trina Solar - Top Global PV Manufacturer for Environmental and Social Commitments, last access 30 April 2015









