Leading the world in solar

	Trina Solar has been manufacturing high quality photovoltaic solar panels since 1997. We are a world’s leading solar supplier, having shipped over 23 gigawatts worldwide, providing clean, affordable and reliable energy to homes, businesses and power plants around the world

Learn more about our companyarrows





 





