(1)











About Trina Solar Energy co Ltd




Established
1997


Headquarters





                                100 Century Center, Suite 501
San Jose, CA
95112 United States









More About Us




More About Us

Founded in 1997, and listed on the New York Stock Exchange in 2006, Trina Solar specializes in the manufacture of crystalline silicon photovoltaic modules and system integration. Trina Solar is not only a pioneer of China's PV industry, but has become an influential shaper of the global solar industry and a leader in solar modules, solutions and services. 





Technology Offered




Technology Offered








                                    Solar PV
                                







Brochure & Media Gallery




Brochure & Media Gallery

(1 of 1)





(1 of 1)








Trina Solar Product Warranty Spec Sheet














Product Manufacturer Ratings by EnergySage




Product Manufacturer Ratings by EnergySage
Learn More


Learn More




Overall Rating:  Standard


• At or weaker than industry average performance, quality, and durability specifications
• Industry average warranty coverage



Warranty Rating:  Standard


• Standard-level performance output and materials warranties



Performance Quality Durability Rating:  Standard


• Efficiency: The majority of Trina's panel models operate within the industry average efficiency range
• Power output: Trina's internal testing indicates that their panels are capable of producing as much power as their power output rating
• Temperature sensitivity: All of Trina's panel models operate within the industry average range of temperature sensitivity
• Quality manufacturing standards: Compliant
• Durability standards: Compliant
• Snow & wind load: Snow load ratings are at industry average; wind load ratings are below industry average






Product Manufacturing Details




Product Manufacturing Details



Current Models And Output
PA05 245-260W, PDG5 245-255W, PD14 290-310W


Product Technology
Polycrystalline


Efficiency
14.1-15.9%


Product warranty duration
10 Years


What's Covered in Product Warranty
Trina Solar's product warranty covers defects in materials and workmanship; covers effects in design, material, workmanship or manufacture that materially impede their functioning and conform to the specifications and the drawings applicable thereto under normal application, installation, use, and service conditions for a period of 10 years after purchase.


Product performance warranty
At the end of 25 Years power output should be no less than 80%.


What's covered in performance warranty
Trina Solar's performance warranty covers the output efficiency of your solar system. After a period of 25 (twenty-five) years output should be no less than 80%. If out is reduced to less than 80% after 25 years then Trina Solar repair or replace the modules.


Where Manufactured?
China


Corporate/Ownership Structure
Private Independent






