    GCL-Poly ramped up its annual polysilicon production capacity to 65,000MT and its wafer production capacity to 8GW as at the end of 2011. As for the PV power station business, the Group owns PV power stations already constructed and to be developed in the U.S., South Africa and China, with aggregated capacity of over 2GW. As for the solar system integration business, the Group provides PV power station investors with one-stop solar system solutions covering project development, design, procurement, construction, financing and operation                                




